N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 33.12 - Restrictions on negotiator's permit

State Regulations
(a) A negotiator permittee shall not offer for sale or solicit any order in this

State for the sale of any alcoholic beverages. (b) Samples of the alcoholic beverages
manufactured or sold by the principal may not be imported into this State until
such permit is obtained. Notes
